These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-1::.
House: wooden, colonial, palace, tower
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, baking, fishing, reading
4 different games are played: chess, go, mah-jongg, bridge
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, reggae, rock, hip-hop
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, dutch, egyptian, argentine
 1. the wooden house is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the egyptian is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 3. the argentine is on the left of the dutch##1
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 6. the egyptian is on the far right##1
 7. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 8. the polish is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 9. the palace house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
10. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
11. the wooden house is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person playing go##2
13. the palace house is the argentine##1
14. the egyptian is the colonial house##1
15. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the colonial house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| House           | wooden | palace | tower  | colonial    |
| Hobby   | baking     | reading   | fishing  | camping  |
| Game           | go        | mah-jongg    | bridge        | chess |
| Music-Genre         | hip-hop    | reggae      | techno   | rock    |
| Nationality     | polish  | argentine     | dutch | egyptian |

