.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, snowmobile, tram, helicopter
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, coral, aquamarine, black
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, canasta, monopoly
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, videographer, entrepreneur, dancer
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, prince, game, cain
 1. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 3. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
 4. the dancer is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is the prince-smoker##1
 6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
 8. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
 9. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
10. the person who likes fuchsia is the cain-smoker##1
11. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
12. the accountant is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
13. the videographer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Transport      | tram        | helicopter       | ship    | snowmobile       |
| Color         | aquamarine | coral      | black | fuchsia |
| Game   | monopoly     | canasta | snooker  | mah-jongg   |
| Job   | videographer   | dancer         | accountant   | entrepreneur      |
| Cigar         | prince      | old-henry     | game    | cain      |

