.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, davidoff, dunhill, swisher
City: san-francisco, nizza, berlin, liverpool
4 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, poker, backgammon
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, poppy, amaryllis, sunflower
House: farmhouse, tower, ranch-style, victorian
 1. the person who growspoppy is the person playing scrabble##1
 2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 3. the victorian house is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
 5. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
 6. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
 7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 8. the farmhouse house is on the right of the victorian house##1
 9. the person who growspoppy is in an odd position##4
10. the dunhill-smoker is the person playing poker##1
11. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
12. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
13. the person who growsamaryllis is the swisher-smoker##1
14. the person playing poker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| Cigar          | dunhill | davidoff | bolivar     | swisher |
| City           | berlin  | liverpool   | san-francisco | nizza  |
