There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water, milk, iced-tea
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, iris, daisy, balloon-flower
City: prague, nizza, new-york, berlin
There 4 different types of food: pepper, kiwi, nectarine, cranberry
 1. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 2. the person who growsdaisy is the alhambra-smoker##1
 3. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
 4. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person eating pepper and the person eating nectarine##2
 5. the person traveling to prague is on the far left##1
 6. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
 7. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
 8. the person traveling to nizza is the person eating kiwi##1
 9. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
10. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
12. the old-henry-smoker is the person drinking iced-tea##1
13. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
14. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
15. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |        4        |
| Cigar         | dannemann | havana    | old-henry | alhambra       |
