 2. the british is in an even position##4
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the british##1
 4. the japanese is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
 8. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
 9. the russian is the person playing snooker##1
10. the person playing poker is the person drinking juice##1
11. the russian is the person drinking sprite##1
12. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person drinking mirinda##1
13. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
14. the person playing poker is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
