 3. the person who likes pink is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 5. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
 6. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 7. the person who likes pink is the person playing billiard##1
 8. the person who likes black is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person playing poker##2
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person traveling to london is in an even position##4
11. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
12. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
13. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
14. the person who likes black is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
